org.webcurator.domain.model.core
Class AuthorisingAgent

java.lang.Object
  org.webcurator.domain.model.core.AbstractIdentityObject
      org.webcurator.domain.model.core.AuthorisingAgent
All Implemented Interfaces:
Annotatable, HasDatabaseIdentity, HasIdentity, HasOid
public class AuthorisingAgent
extends AbstractIdentityObject
implements Annotatable

Represents an Agent responsible for granting permission to harvest a site and provide permission for access. An authorising agent may directly own or manage the website being harvested, or may be something like Government legislation that is offerring blanket permission to a Library to harvest content within a particular domain space.
